Introduction

Jang Woohyuk, also known as his DJ name XXXV is a South Korean rapper, singer, choreographer, and DJ under WH Creative. He is best known for being a member of the boy group H.O.T.. Following their disbandment in May 2001, he, along with former members Tony An and Lee Jae Won, formed the group jtL.

Following jtL's disbandment in 2003, he debuted as a solo artist on September 12, 2005, with the album No More Drama.
